description:
Q-Free Intrada© ALPR is a software library for automatic license plate recognition (ALPR/ANPR). Intrada© is used world wide in high-speed tolling systems and traffic and surveillance systems. Intrada ALPR supports over 150 countries and states and is developed, maintained and supported by a team of 15 experts. 

    This .NET library offers access to the Intrada© ALPR engines with all the advantages of the .NET framework and languages. Intrada© ALPR for .NET has  been designed to scale in a multi-threaded environment, enabling the possibilities of parallel OCR processing. 

    Note that this library does not include the core Intrada© engines which are required to test and deploy. You can request your free trial license on https://intrada.q-free.com/net-license-request

summary: Intrada ALPR is a professional software library for automatic license plate recognition (ALPR/ANPR). This .NET package provides an easy-to-use API and excellent scaling options for ALPR-enabled applications.
